title: Last Testament
author: AbbotAlban
pages:
#- THE LAST WILL AND TESTAMENT OF
ABBOT ALBAN, ABBOT OF BRESLAUER ABBEY AND HEAD PRIEST OF THE CHURCH OF ST WALPURAGA.
#- In this tomb lies the remains of Abbot Alban, founder and builder of the Church of St Walpurga and the attached Breslauer Abbey, humble and devoted servant of God.
#- I leave my Church and it's holdings in both land and wealth to the Kingdom of Prussia under the Kaiser of the Holy Krautchan Empire in the knowledge that it's existence and history will be preserved.
#- Glory to God in the highest.





AbbotAlban,
11/4/15
#- 